member.name: CERT_X942_DH_PARAMETERS
member.summary: The CERT_X942_DH_PARAMETERS structure contains parameters associated with a Diffie-Hellman public key algorithm.

member.name: CERT_X942_DH_PARAMETERS.p
member.summary: Prime modulus P. The most significant bit of the most significant byte must always be set to 1.

member.name: CERT_X942_DH_PARAMETERS.g
member.summary: Generator G. Must be the same length as p (must be padded with 0x00 bytes if it is less).

summary.para: A factor of p–1. The most significant bit of the most significant byte must be set to 1.

member.name: CERT_X942_DH_PARAMETERS.pValidationParams
member.summary: Optional pointer to a structure. If the cbData member of the q BLOB is zero, all of the members of pValidationParams must be zero.
